{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"党旗下站起新一代","authors":["张宝申"],"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":6,"day":27}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"党旗下站起新一代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京永定机械厂　张宝申"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗外，行行杨柳迎风摆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋内，支部大会正召开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉火欢呼眨眼笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锻锤咚咚直喝采。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党旗下站起新一代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威风凛凛好气派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢的性格钢的胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就象刚跃出熔炉的红钢块。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进厂时红卫兵袖章臂上戴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓言伴着杨柳栽："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“阳光雨露哺育咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比一比看谁长得快！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨里树苗往上窜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争中新人长成材，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学马列，眼亮善辨钢与渣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打硬仗，重担上肩身不歪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反击右倾翻案风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵战鼓传天外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火线上填写志愿书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字蘸满恨和爱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗外杨柳迎风摆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党旗下一代新人接班来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江河奔腾浪推浪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着朝阳奔入海……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}